
hotcolormap(1)                 Scilab Function                 hotcolormap(1)
NAME
  hotcolormap - red to yellow colormap

CALLING SEQUENCE
  cmap=hotcolormap(n)

PARAMETERS

  n     : integer >= 3, the colormap size.

  cmap  : matrix with 3 columns [R,G,B].

DESCRIPTION
  hotcolormap computes a colormap with n hot colors varying from red to yel-
  low.

EXAMPLE
  xset("colormap",hotcolormap(32))
  plot3d1()

SEE ALSO
  colormap, graycolormap, xset
